posting_body: ['Dockside', '23605 62nd Ave S, Kent, WA, 98032', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'WELCOME TO DOCKSIDE APARTMENTS', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 760 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Dockside Apartment Homes is located in the premier Lakes neighborhood in Kent, Washington.', 'We offer richly appointed one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'Our unique newly renovated homes feature a luxurious white modern kitchen with warm gray cabinets, stainless steel appliances, vinyl flooring a washer and dryer in every home.', 'Residents enjoy basketball and racquetball in our indoor court, two resort style pools and a business center.', 'Waterford at the Lakes is minutes from thriving employers such as Showare Center, Kent Station, REI Corporate headquarters and Boeing, as well as I-5 and Hwy-167.', 'Our pet friendly community offers a picturesque setting, featuring classically styled buildings surrounded by mature tree-lined streets, tranquil lakes and unsurpassed amenities.', 'Visit us today for a personal tour!', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and Dogs Allowed .There is a $500 pet deposit ($200 is refundable).', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Pit Bulls, Doberman, Rottweiler, & Cane Corso or any mix with these breeds.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday, Wednesday and Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday and Thursday: 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', '3YztnoBB']
